video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192290/extras/1618d2ca50419a89d10cbd9e141d64fe.poster.avif?t=1773972352\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192290/extras/1618d2ca50419a89d10cbd9e141d64fe.webm?t=1773972352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192290/extras/1618d2ca50419a89d10cbd9e141d64fe.mp4?t=1773972352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在即將被發現的瞬間，必須做出2選1的選擇↓↓↓</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192290/extras/0d8226d4be24a0536a69857a8675478d.poster.avif?t=1773972352\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192290/extras/0d8226d4be24a0536a69857a8675478d.webm?t=1773972352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192290/extras/0d8226d4be24a0536a69857a8675478d.mp4?t=1773972352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >結果會是「成功逃脫」還是「被抓住懲罰」呢！？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192290/extras/cd6c706db8c662c1aa04b86619a802ea.avif?t=1773972352\" width=616 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一邊享受緊張的氣氛，一邊逐漸進行更大膽的露出自慰。<br>做出這樣的公然猥褻行為，一旦被發現就會被以各種手段懲罰。<br>只要一被發現＝本番插入性愛！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・H場景CG 7枚，搭配豐富的立繪與差分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・遊戲中的事件劇情女主角全語音。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・隨著一次次的露出挑戰，逐漸變化的H狀態。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・「逃走」還是「留下來」，真白的命運由你來決定！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・遊戲通關後可於房間內解鎖全CG回想。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・遊戲本體結束後還有自由模式可以讓真白繼續在街上玩露出遊戲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192290/extras/5e253c6029134ecbdb5842eb1dcd1caf.poster.avif?t=1773972352\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192290/extras/5e253c6029134ecbdb5842eb1dcd1caf.webm?t=1773972352\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192290/extras/5e253c6029134ecbdb5842eb1dcd1caf.mp4?t=1773972352\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >共有8個露出場景</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・公園裡：在無人的樹叢裡露出自慰忍住不叫出來。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・住宅區：一邊警戒著有沒有人出現，在露出的同時故意大聲發出聲音。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・路燈下：露出胸部和陰部嘗試放置Play。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・書店裡：在內褲裡放入跳蛋，在18禁專區來回游走。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・森林中：帶著貓耳露出散步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・大學裡：在就讀的大學裡用桌腳自慰，在男廁裡放尿。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・便利商店：對著店員誘惑一般的春光乍洩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・投幣洗衣機店：把全身的衣服丟進洗衣機，在洗完之前都只能一絲不掛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >人物介紹</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >～清宮　真白～</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最普通的不能再普通的女大學生。<br>沒有什麼和異性交往的經驗，所有的色色知識都是從網路上學到的處女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高潮的時候一定會忍不住失禁。自從第一次嘗試野外露出以來，<br>怎麼在公共場所暴露，怎樣的甜美高潮大放尿就成為腦中揮之不去的幻想。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這樣的我，應該還是算個…<br>普通的大學生的吧？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192290/extras/e524672ab410b85d5b1475dbc8667d19.poster.avif?t=1773972352\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3192290/extras/e524672ab410b85d5b1475dbc8667d19.webm?